
'''Kevin Okyere''' yɛ Ghananii  a w'abo ne ho moden ofangoo adwuma wɔ Ghana. W'a bue adwuma a wɔfrƐ no  Springfield Energy- opipipiipiii adwuma a wɔ tu fangoo. Wo te adwuma no wɔ [[2008]].

== Abrabo ne Sukuu ==
Wɔ woo no 1980, wɔ akukudam abusua mu .Mpo sɛ woyƐ odufuo mpo no,na wɔtoon nsua sɛ dia ɛbɛyɛ a wo bɛ bua won a wɔ bɛ hwɛ footbal agokensieɛ wɔ Kumasi Agorɔ pɔn keseɛ.

wɔ kɔɔ sukuu wɔ Opoku Ware Senior High School,wɔ wie yɛ no ,wɔ tu kwan kɔɔ amanoni kɔ tua ne sukuu so wɔ George Mason University in Virginia.

== Abasobodeɛ ==
Kevin's adwuma Springfield nyaa kyɛfa wɔ West Cape Three Points ɛfa mmienu fre Ghana aban wɔ 2016 abraa Kosmos wie won adwuma die. N'adwuma no di me wɔ fangoo tu mo wɔ Mali ne Burkina Faso ne Nigeria fangoo. Wɔ ma nu abandin wɔ Emy Africa abosobodeɛ dwuma a na wɔ yɛ Barima a afe mu no wɔ bo ne ho mmodin wɔ fangoo dwumadie mo.{{Reflist}}
